comments: Used online textbooks tools extensively. Felt like a junior high class where you had to search the textbook looking for answers, but didn\'t actually learn anything. Was really disappointed, especially for a capstone class.
Project management J-term class. Very knowledgable with tons of real world experience. Highly recommended if you are in PM or want to get into it.

J-Term class. Excellent Professor. Does Project Mgmt in the real world. Was given short notice to teach class and did great. Explains topics very well. One large project assigned. Everyone I talked to liked the class and felt they learned a lot. Highly recommend Prof if she teaches this course again!
